From: sattler@news.cs.TU-Magdeburg.DE (Kai-Uwe Sattler)
Subject: [ANNOUNCE] Shared libs for InterViews
Date: 13 Sep 1993 11:16:36 +0200

The shared libraries for InterViews 3.1 (libIV and libUnidraw) are
on ftp.cs.tu-magdeburg.de (141.44.21.200, 141.44.20.21) in 
/pub/linux/local.
There are also doc and idraw (linked with the DLL).

I have tested the library with all IV examples. Only the morpher doesn't
work.

Have fun !
